Dorsal-fin rays 39-45 (Table 1), tips of anterior 4-8 rays projecting from fin membrane, anterior 5 rays uniserial and unsegmented, more posterior rays biserial and segmented; all rays simple. Anteriormost dorsal-fin ray supported by two pterygiophores; 
